headline: The Smartest Dividend Stocks to Buy With $5,000 Right Now
summary: Sysco sells and distributes food and related products to customers and has been increasing its dividend for 56 years.  Johnson & Johnson produces consumer and pharmaceutical products and has raised its dividends for 63 consecutive years.  Coca-Cola has also paid out higher dividends for 63 consecutive years.
